---
title: Sugar-Rubbed Pork Chops with Caramelized Root Vegetables
description: A sweet and spicy sugar rub makes these pork chops unreasonably delectable. Served with caramelized parsnips, carrots, and pearl onions, this dish strikes the perfect balance of savory and sweet. A simple drizzle of pan sauce takes this recipe from delicious to restaurant-worthy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54ff26476ced6e0b068b456b.jpg
